-- BP Will Send Crude to Other Platforms If Planned Gulf Relief Wells Fail
-- Jessica Resnick-Ault
-- 2010-06-28T15:00:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/bp-will-send-crude-to-other-platforms-if-planned-gulf-relief-wells-fail.html

          
          
             BP Plc will send more oil to other
platforms to reduce the amount pouring into the Gulf of Mexico
if its planned relief wells fail to plug the leak.  
 Kent Wells, BP senior vice president, spoke on a conference
call today.  
          
          


  


        